 Cloud Computing
 &lt;a href="#cloud-computing" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink to this heading"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3 id="definition" class="heading-link"&gt;
 Definition
 &lt;a href="#definition" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink to this heading"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cloud computing lets you use servers, storage, and applications on the Internet instead of owning or managing your own hardware. It’s an easy, flexible, and cost-effective way to get the technology you need without the hassle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;






